UNGQONGQOSHE wezeMpilo kuzwelonke uDkt Zweli Mkhize usememezele ukuthi sesinyukele ku-34 357 isibalo sabantu osekuqinisekisiwe ukuthi bahaqwe yiCovid-19 kuleli. UMkhize umemezele izibalo zakamuva ngoMsombuluko ntambama kanti uveze ukuthi nesibalo sabashonile sinyukele ku-705. "EWestern Cape kushone abanye abantu abawu-22, okubeke isabalo sabashonile ku-525 kulesi sifundazwe. Sidlulisa amazwi enduduzo emndenini yabashonile, sifisa nokubonga abasebenzi bezempilo abebebanakekele ezibhedlela," kusho uMkhize. UNgqongqoshe uthe sebewu-16 808 abantu asebesindile kwiCovi-19 kuleli. Uthe sebebalelwa ngaphezulu kuka-740 000 abantu asebehlolelwe leli gciwane kuleli. As of today, the cumulative number of confirmed #COVID19 cases is 34 357, the total number of deaths is 705 and total recoveries are now 16 808 pic.twitter.com/G2zKOUhUUR Officially opening the Thusong Field Hospital, Khayelitsha. pic.twitter.com/mTSCyWllKC